text:
@WhiteHouse @realDonaldTrump nice he finally got
around to it
eh?
I mean,
he's KNOWN about
#COVID19
since JANUARY!
He had ALL OF JANUARY.
ALL OF FEBRUARY.
He could have WARNED US.
He didn't.
This is the BIGGEST #CoverUp
in American History!

Now,
he wants us to, what?
Be grateful?

too little
too late. https://t.co/i2JvRYP76m
